                                                            <th class="text-center vertical-header" style="width:8%; border-color:black !important;">No. of days of lay-off</th>
                                                            <th class="text-center vertical-header" style="width:6%; border-color:black !important;">No. of days of maternity leave with</th>
                                                            <th class="text-center vertical-header" style="width:8%; border-color:black !important;">No. of days leave with wages enjoyed</th>
                                                            <th class="text-center vertical-header" style="width:8%; border-color:black !important;">No Of Leave Without Pay</th>
